column3: “Another great strain by Bedford Grow! Worked great for pain and was a good upbeat buzz.”
“3rd coast Panama chunk is other great strain by bedford grow. They are putting some of the best product out there for Illinois medical patients”
“Smells fruity and sweet. Tastes earthy and smooth with a pleasant aftertaste. Provided me with nice relaxing more of an indica feeling. Strong, worth trying.”
“It’s great! Makes you forget your pain and stress!”
“Very tasty hybrid that is more of a sativa energy. It's tasty and relieved my anxiety.”
“Very relaxing yet still energetic. Would definitely repurchase”
“Uplifting high that relieves all anxiety for hours. Well worth the time!”
“Technically a 3.5. Mellow and stony but not quite faded.”
